trans-unit.source: This class identifies properties, not the values of properties.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen identifiserer egenskaper, ikke verdiene for egenskaper.

trans-unit.source: Static objects of this type are found as fields of <xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElement> and control pattern classes.
trans-unit.target: Statiske objekter av denne typen finnes som felt for <xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElement>og kontrollere mønsteret klasser.</xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElement>

trans-unit.source: Retrieves an <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.AutomationProperty"></xref> that encapsulates a specified numerical identifier.
trans-unit.target: Henter en <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.AutomationProperty"> </xref> som innkapsler angitte identifikator.

trans-unit.source: Normally, properties are identified by an <xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationProperty> object.

This method can be used to create such an object when only the numerical identifier (the <xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationIdentifier.Id%2A> inherited from <xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationIdentifier>) is known.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden kan brukes til å opprette slikt objekt når bare numerisk identifikator (den <xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationIdentifier.Id%2A>arvet fra <xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationIdentifier>) er kjent.</xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationIdentifier> </xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationIdentifier.Id%2A>

trans-unit.source: Retrieves an <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.AutomationProperty"></xref> that encapsulates a specified numerical identifier.
trans-unit.target: Henter en <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.AutomationProperty"> </xref> som innkapsler angitte identifikator.
